  "text": "Remark 1.11. In dimension m = 2, the local smooth interior estimates as in (1.7) were obtained in [CITATION_1] using classical methods but for smooth Dirac-harmonic maps and assuming also that ψ L 4 (B1) ≤ ǫ. ",
